### **Summary of ASX Announcement (Form 604 – Change in Substantial Holding)**  

- **Substantial Holder:** Ivanhoe Capital Holdings Pte Ltd  
- **Change in Holding:** Increased stake from **14.36%** (11,977,801 shares) to **19.94%** (21,977,801 shares) via **placement participation**.  
- **Transaction Details:** Acquired **10,000,000 shares** at **$0.30 per share** (total **$3,000,000**).  
- **Date of Change:** **23 June 2025**.  

**No other material information identified.**
